description:
Paul Oakenfold: Perfecto On Tour Full

DVD/CD/MP3

Renowned DJ and producer Paul Oakenfold spins all over the globe and he brings it to SIRIUS XM with his weekly show Paul Oakenfold: Perfecto On Tour. Oakenfold, who has remixed records for artists including Madonna, Dave Matthews Band, Justin Timberlake, Elvis Presley and U2, delivers his world famous sets every week. Paul Oakenfold is taking you global with Perfecto On Tour.
